*Request Background*

Currently Confluence HTML export shipped out Confluence style sheet with it and it generate great HTML pages for users to use. However it still doesn't provide a header and footer that looks like Confluence layout.

It would be great if we could provide an HTML export that looks a lot more similar to Confluence page.

